Enum GradientOrientation

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<GradientOrientation>
      • org.pepstock.charba.client.colors.GradientOrientation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<GradientOrientation>, Key

    public enum GradientOrientation
extends java.lang.Enum<GradientOrientation>
implements Key
    Represents the gradient orientation for gradient.
    Every orientation contains also on which gradient type can be applied.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
